verbose_text: Interestingly, most of these factors were either patient related (i.e., Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group or ECOG and KPS) [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR], liver related (i.e., serum albumin level, serum lactate dehydrogenase or LDH, and Child-Pugh classification) [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], or metastatic related (visceral metastasis, other extrahepatic metastasis other than bone metastases) characteristics [XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR].
